---
title: BBQ Glazed Chicken Bowls with Cajun-Inspired Rice
description: This meal is full of robust American Southwest-inspired flavours - Southwest spiced chicken gets baked with a BBQ glaze and there's some extra for drizzling on top! Our Cajun-style dirty rice is fragrant and speckled with sweet corn.
